  "2026-06-03T23:25:32.486Z",codex,"Feature 1: registerItemFields now declares github_author/github_created_at/github_updated_at; import emits a github_author:<login> tag and enriches the description with author + created/updated ISO timestamps (additive). Verified on a real 106-item import of unbraind/pm-cli."
  "2026-06-03T23:25:32.646Z",codex,"Feature 2: parseRateLimit/formatRateLimit parse X-RateLimit-Remaining/Limit/Reset case-insensitively; pm github validate --repo surfaces quota + warns when low. Verified live: quota 4900/5000 reported."
  "2026-06-03T23:25:32.805Z",codex,"Feature 3: --skip-drafts excludes draft PRs (isDraftPr) when --include-prs set. Unit-tested; live import accepted the flag."
